---
title: Smart Honey-Lemon and Dill Chicken with Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Feta
description: Chicken gets a zesty and sweet treatment from lemon and honey and — as if that wasn't enough — it's finished with feta, almonds and dill! A warm and comforting salad of sweet potatoes and spring mix tossed in a shallot vinaigrette makes for a flavourful side.
